ADDITIONAL CONTEXT (not part of the legal license, but required reading)

This project documents a methodology for distilling a public Bilibili streamer's
speaking style into LLM system prompts (SOUL.md + SKILL.md). The streamer in
question (明前奶绿 / Mingqian Milk Green) has publicly stated:

  - Her voice / audio works are commercial-use forbidden ("音声禁止商用")
  - Non-commercial derivative creation (二次创作) is permitted

This LICENSE (CC-BY-NC-4.0) aligns with that stance:
  - You MAY use these prompts for non-commercial research, fan-made AI
    companions, methodology study, or further derivative creation
  - You MAY NOT use these prompts in commercial products, paid services, or
    any monetized deployment without explicit permission from the streamer

If 明前奶绿 herself, her management (if any), or Laplace-related affiliates
request takedown, the maintainer will comply immediately.

For attribution, please cite:
  colourfulmaster/milkgreen-skill (2026). milkGreenSoul methodology.
  https://github.com/colourfulmaster/milkgreen-skill
